{"tid":2303714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子花27萬要求娶處女　洞房驚見妊娠紋　怒告婚姻介紹所！","createTime":"2020-11-28T07:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T13:22:15.000Z","uid":209657,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"454ff1daa219f571b384ec7012b95b057dfba283","tid":2303714,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/oHiWBv-_4FtJMozrtLnRI7Gr2c4=/760x566/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5CJCOLJETEH54FKV7DDETUB6CA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoHiWBv-_4FtJMozrtLnRI7Gr2c4%3D%2F760x566%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5CJCOLJETEH54FKV7DDETUB6CA.jpg&h=db4b8bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高雄一名林姓男子為了尋找結婚對象，透過婚友社幫忙介紹，想要找到「高中學歷的處女」，後來認識了陸籍的趙姓女子，5天後火速結婚，沒想到準備辦事時，竟發現趙女肚子上有妊娠紋，而且也不是高中學歷，氣得提起告訴。<br />\n<br />\n現年51歲的林男提告指出，2009年他透過婚友社介紹，花了20幾萬從中國廣西省桂林迎娶趙姓女子回台灣。事後他認為自己被婚友社騙、被趙女氣到，因為趙女根本沒有高中學歷，而且肚子爬滿妊娠紋，明顯生過小孩，根本不是處女；<br />\n<br />\n加上趙女來台後就外出工作，每天跟同事傳十幾封簡訊，又常常外出鬼混，因此認為婚友社違約、趙女公司沒有管理好員工，讓他婚姻失敗而失眠痛苦、精神崩潰、無心工作，提告求償150萬元。"},{"pid":"c39119e21979bbde3c330cf03fc630dd64c838f6","tid":2303714,"uid":122134,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"幼稚園啦"},{"pid":"cac7dba3d8a0a19f7f4f15f359985208fbcec58e","tid":2303714,"uid":364850,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:29:32.000Z","msg":"詐騙真心仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過幾萬蚊就想娶處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab9d305211ac300bde217fa938fb82b56540f66","tid":2303714,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"判決書指出，林男為了找尋適合的對象，於2009年12月21日與該婚姻介紹協會接觸，繳了5萬元的會費，簽訂了相關合約，想要找到高中學歷，並且是處女的女子結婚。林男當年12月26日受邀前往大陸廣西，參加聯誼活動，期間與趙姓女子聊得十分開心，因此付了22萬8960元給介紹協會，過了5天後，就與趙女在當地結婚。<br />\n<br />\n不過，林男準備與趙女享受魚水之歡，卻發現對方肚子上有妊娠紋，也非高中學歷，介紹協會還浮報費用，並且什麼服務項目都沒有做，更不滿婚介協會沒有事先考察背景、做身體檢查，害自己「誤會」與趙女結婚，決定將介紹協會告上法院。"},{"pid":"fa7ebf9fbab207ba470b7d11bc807e7fd17ad0fc","tid":2303714,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"對此，介紹協會則反駁，林男與趙女認識的過程，社團都沒有干預，是他們自由戀愛，根本沒辦法知道對方是不是高中學歷，更別說得知是否為處女了，當然不負賠償責任，也沒有不當得利。<br />\n<br />\n法官審理此案時，認為男子沒有提出證據，證明協會侵害配偶權、或是人格法益受損，且就算一開始有提出娶妻條件，但內容有背於公共秩序或善良風俗，明顯違背民法第72條，最後判決男子敗訴。"},{"pid":"fa46698326302a33a219534ccf12091d50360cef","tid":2303714,"uid":25514,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"做左大半世人仲唔撚化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafb3bf9a69d71854affccae933fd4c116791da5","tid":2303714,"uid":42044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"高中仲係處女？"},{"pid":"2ce52772d86a1b271cea58dd042f756eaf45de7b","tid":2303714,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會係減咗肥咋?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肚臍都未必係處啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0f97dcfca0daff75eb9c7276b063bc3f915771","tid":2303714,"uid":211878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"好撚離譜喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce9eb934e525fa32b45761dcd06ff0f1bf3b8f6","tid":2303714,"uid":165336,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"你話條女隱瞞就話姐<br />\n簽哂約收哂錢都唔同條女驗身<br />\n係咪睇死毒撚唔敢搞你<br />\n就斷鳩估俾隻支那雞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85af57a47d56aac3696f0fb415375fd2dfdf994f","tid":2303714,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"一生人一次為咗哩一晚應該準備咗好耐，究竟有幾大創傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439aef4dbe1f4d8508c7f7c12daf4129a767b4c6","tid":2303714,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"網名叫「處女」都唔算？"},{"pid":"a6dce7b73a224004bb09ef60e275b301364c24a0","tid":2303714,"uid":259901,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:15:59.000Z","msg":"屌，冇錢就咪學人買新樓啦<br />\n而家有棟樓比你住，雖然層樓死過人係凶宅，但仲有咩好唔滿意先，有得住就偷笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a800eaff84419e116efca0588be55ea6bcdd4274","tid":2303714,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064b3d1efcfee370b50a5954af346403e7f46b44","tid":2303714,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ce52772d86a1b271cea58dd042f756eaf45de7b","tid":2303714,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會係減咗肥咋?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肚臍都未必係處啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"肥仔都有妊娠紋<br />\n一定係大過肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1008c0995b7bc2c88a6e518aacf05969bca44426","tid":2303714,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"重點係又係大陸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13037088398080876d270df98f9a9172e083ef8","tid":2303714,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"娶妻求處女"},{"pid":"544c62a74b20d6a2c808a39d2d40e5be71fb50c2","tid":2303714,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6dce7b73a224004bb09ef60e275b301364c24a0","tid":2303714,"uid":259901,"l